{"tid":2210973,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"(減肥) 168斷食+Weekdays減糖減澱粉","createTime":"2020-09-20T21:38:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T05:37:23.000Z","uid":100499,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"3d354a5a5cb6d13917ac6360ed8e6b316add88d7","tid":2210973,"uid":100499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T21:38:30.000Z","msg":"最近四個月都實行緊168斷食(1-9pm先食嘢)；Weekdays食清(戒糖，澱粉，飯2L水或以上)；Weekend隨便食(乜都食，平時有嘢想食就趁星期六日先食)，因為想減肥減得開心<br />\n<br />\n然後，我一星期已經去四日gym，主要跑歩機，太空滑歩機，划艇機，但好似都無乜減到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個肚腩仲好大<br />\n<br />\n有咩我可以再改善？"},{"pid":"eb1cee37ea7943200c2c873fce48f413a6687f7b","tid":2210973,"uid":33728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T21:39:05.000Z","msg":"不"},{"pid":"3f0240472cbfc8a74cfffe246d5b9abbee56c8c2","tid":2210973,"uid":25487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T21:43:04.000Z","msg":"會唔會係weekend太放縱？<br />\n<br />\n如果減左醣再加168，點都會輕幾磅架喎～"},{"pid":"ace753c2bbc95a1ccaf48c3f8e11a1919c513ea8","tid":2210973,"uid":161057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d354a5a5cb6d13917ac6360ed8e6b316add88d7","tid":2210973,"uid":100499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T21:38:30.000Z","msg":"最近四個月都實行緊168斷食(1-9pm先食嘢)；Weekdays食清(戒糖，澱粉，飯2L水或以上)；Weekend隨便食(乜都食，平時有嘢想食就趁星期六日先食)，因為想減肥減得開心<br />\n<br />\n然後，我一星期已經去四日gym，主要跑歩機，太空滑歩機，划艇機，但好似都無乜減到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個肚腩仲好大<br />\n<br />\n有咩我可以再改善？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T22:07:00.000Z","msg":"Ching可以試下 星期1-3食小野, 4-5medium, 六日照返而家咁，再加埋每兩日做15分鐘hiit"},{"pid":"553f5fdb097adf8a5edabe925b461db8527ac09a","tid":2210973,"uid":189109,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T22:15:16.000Z","msg":"跑多啲低intensity步 睇下低心率跑法 MAF180<br />\n我同你一樣，全個禮拜除星期日